going to be used for SEO. 

320
00:18:23.020 --> 00:18:24.957
So just keep in mind that, 

321
00:18:24.957 --> 00:18:26.965
when you're hiding content, 

322
00:18:26.965 --> 00:18:30.025
you need to keep things 
