323
00:18:30.025 --> 00:18:32.352
That same content that maybe 

324
00:18:32.352 --> 00:18:34.598
is hidden from visual users 

325
00:18:34.598 --> 00:18:38.425
needs to be kind of 
represented in some way. 

326
00:18:38.425 --> 00:18:40.902
Especially internal links, 

327
00:18:40.902 --> 00:18:44.756
because those are 
very important for SEO. 

328
00:18:44.756 --> 00:18:47.063
Media Optimization: 

329
00:18:47.063 --> 00:18:51.848
One of the things 
that SEOs talk about 

330
00:18:51.848 --> 00:18:55.725
whenever accessibility comes up

331
00:18:55.725 --> 00:18:58.852
is alt tags for images. 

332
00:18:58.852 --> 00:19:05.166
SEOs tend to like to optimize 
alt text for images, 

333
00:19:05.166 --> 00:19:08.137
because search engines 

334
00:19:08.137 --> 00:19:13.434
utilize the text 
found in alt attributes 

335
00:19:13.434 --> 00:19:16.749
to associate keywords 

336
00:19:16.749 --> 00:19:19.432
for an understanding of the image. 

337
00:19:19.432 --> 00:19:21.806
I think initially, 

338
00:19:21.806 --> 00:19:24.500
when search engines 
started doing this, 

339
00:19:24.500 --> 00:19:26.996
it was a really great idea, 

340
00:19:26.996 --> 00:19:29.465
because if you 
use the alt tags 

341
00:19:29.465 --> 00:19:30.934
